  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ファッション業界のパーティー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Fashion industry party",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 1.6333332936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "初めまして、franと申します！\nあ、テレビで見て下さってるんですか、光栄です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you‚ my name is fran!\nOh‚ you're watching me on TV‚ it's an honor!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.466666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。こちらこそお会い出来て嬉しいです\nよろしければ、お名刺をいただいても？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. I'm glad to meet you\nIf you don't mind‚ can I have your business card?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0999999444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.2333332777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "なぜアイドルがこのパーティーに参加したか？\nえっと……私、ファッション業界に興味があって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did idol attend this party?\nUmm… I'm interested in fashion industry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2333332777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "……実は以前ブランドも持っていたんです\n本当ですか！？　ぜひ何かありましたらお声がけ下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Actually‚ I had a brand before\nReally!? If you need anything‚ please let me know",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.566666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.25
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "（あーあ、疲れた……。ファッション業界の人に）\n（顔売れるかなって参加してみたけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah-ah‚ I'm tired…. I tried participating to see）\n（if my face would sell to people in fashion industry…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.333337601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.6000042677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "（えーと、今日もらった名刺は……と）\n（全然、ろくなやつがいないわね……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ummー‚ the business card I got today… is）\n（There aren't any good guys here at all…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6000042677,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2349.9957323000017
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "（この名刺は確か、蛍光色の服着た経営者で）\n（こっちは語尾に「にょ」って付ける自称クリエイター）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This business card is definitely of‚ a manager wearing fluorescent clothes.）\n（This is a self-styled creator who adds 'nyo' to the end of sentences）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9666709344,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6866.662398899997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.533337601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "（ああもう、人の顔なんて一発で覚えられる訳ないわ）\n（大体、パーティーって嫌いなのよね！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh really‚ there's no way I can remember a person's face all at once）\n（Generally‚ I hate parties!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.533337601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "（ブランド復活って目的がなければ）\n（こんな所、絶対に来ないんだから！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After the brand is revived‚ if I don't have a purpose）\n（I'll never come to a place‚ like this!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.8000042677,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6657322999954
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 76.8666709344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、え、わ、私ですか？　こんにちは、はじ……………\nえ、ご、ご無沙汰してます！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ uh‚ is‚ is me? Hello‚ nice to…\nEh‚ it's‚ it's been a while!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8666709344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 85.8666709344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "（突然背後から声掛けるなんて常識なさ過ぎじゃない？）\n（でも……向こうはこっちのこと知ってるみたいね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Isn't it so lacking in common sense to suddenly talk to someone from behind?）\n（But… it seems that side know about this side）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8666709344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "（前にどこかで会ったかしら……）\n（ ああもう、特徴なさ過ぎて全然思い出せない！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder if we've met before somewhere…）\n（Oh really‚ it's so few features that I can't remember it!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1000042677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 102.8000042677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。え、『山田社長』？　山田って言う……な\nじゃなくて……kanaちゃんは元気か……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. Eh‚ \"President Yamada\"? Don't call me Yama…\nNo‚ I mean… is kana-chan doing… well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8000042677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "というか、なんで私の本名を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or rather‚ how do you know my real name…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.433337601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 117.8666709344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "……え、ええ、今日お会い出来て本当に良かったです\nkanaも元気です、今日は旅ロケに行ってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ yes-yes‚ it was really good meeting you today\nkana is also doing well. She is on a location today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8666709344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 126.3000042677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "（あー……思い出した……）\n（kanaに誘われて行ったパーティーで会った人かも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ahー… I remembered…）\n（Maybe it's someone I met at the party kana invited me to）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3000042677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaが面白がってパーティー中ずっと『山田社長』）\n（って呼び続けてたせいで、そのまま覚えられてたんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Maybe it's because kana kept calling me \"President Yamada\" ）\n（during the party for fun‚ and he remembered it as it was）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7000042677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 141.933337601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、それでは失礼します\n今度お会いした時は、ゆっくりお話しさせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ then excuse me\nNext time we meet‚ let's talk about it more carefully!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.933337601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 148.933337601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "（……あー、危なかった。あの人、結構なお偉いさんだし）\n（ 顔を忘れてたなんて失礼、絶対に出来ないもの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Ahー‚ that was dangerous. That person is of quite high-up）\n（It's rude to have forgotten his face‚ it's something I could never do）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.933337601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_01-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaのお陰で思い出したなんて）\n（絶対に、本人には言ってやらないけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can't believe I remembered it thanks to kana）\n（I will never tell her‚ though）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.933337601,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}